OL,3,CCumbria set to elect mayor next year
OL,5,FCumbria is set to have an elected
OL,6,Fmayor in place in May next year.
OL,8,FThe county has been selected as one of
OL,9,Fsix areas on the Government's
OL,10,FDevolution Priority Programme with the
OL,11,Faim of an election in 2026.
OL,13,FThis is after both Cumberland Council
OL,14,Fand Westmorland & Furness council
OL,15,Fsigned up for fast-track devolution
OL,16,Flast month.
OL,18,FThe announcement was made today by
OL,19,FDeputy Prime Minister Angela Rayner.
