OL,3,CCumbria set to elect mayor next year
OL,5,F"While devolution can sound techie,
OL,6,Fthe outcome is simple - it's a plan
OL,7,Ffor putting more money in people's
OL,8,Fpockets, it's a plan for quicker,
OL,9,Fbetter, cheaper transport designed
OL,10,Fwith local people in mind, a plan for
OL,11,Fputting politics back in the service
OL,12,Fof working people."
OL,14,FThe Government says the aim of further
OL,15,Fdevolution is to improve decision-
OL,16,Fmaking by giving more local
OL,17,Fresponsibility to regions over issues
OL,18,Fsuch as transport, housing and
OL,19,Feconomic development.
